      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3404 - Dawud ibn Sirhan asked Abu Abdullah (as):\nAbout a guarantor (kafil) and a pledge (rahn) in a deferred sale (bay' al-nasi'ah).\nImam (as) said: \"There is no harm in it.\""
